么还有人选择燃油车，「完全不理解，怎么现在还有人买油车？油车除了能闻点汽油味，别的还有什么好？」并表示称有充电焦虑的，基本都是汽油车用户操电动车的心。 信息来源：蔚来李斌：不理解为什么还有人买油车 就为了闻汽油味？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c1af236e2ffebf924dab8f3462face16_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "502 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/507211888"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I9JD/0rTV5qNkEAMaCDc0OTk1MzQ5IJWt/40GMAA45A1ABHIJNTA3MjExODg4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1640051903.1854215", "card_id": "Q_507402706", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 211}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待薇娅微博、抖音均被封号，淘宝店铺已「关店处理」，带来哪些警示？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "网络主播一姐黄薇（网名：薇娅）因偷逃税致歉后，其在淘宝、抖音、微博等多个平台的账号被封。 12 月 20 日，澎湃新闻记者查询发现，薇娅在微博、抖音两大社交媒体的账号均被封。其中微博账号显示：「该账号因被投诉违反法律法规和《微博社区公约》的相关规定，现已无法查看。」抖音账号也搜不到相关用户。薇娅微博、抖音均被封号，淘宝店铺已「关店处理」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-fbd98184b12d00dff635d89fcaed446d_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "447 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/507402706"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I9JD/0rTV5qNkEAMaCDc1MDM3NzIwINGxgo4GMAA4hwdABXIJNTA3NDAyNzA2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1640051903.186099", "card_id": "Q_507116648", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 195}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "美剧《切尔诺贝利》拍的怎么样？为何能获得高分？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-6ddc355423c9c0bf2807289e05607f43_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "435 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/507116648"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I9JD/0rTV5qNkEAMaCDc0OTc0MjAxIIXY+40GMAA4wwJABnIJNTA3MTE2NjQ4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "styl